<Layout title="One Computer | Solusi IT & Servis Terpercaya">
    <main class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center px-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-neutral-950 text-neutral-300 selection:bg-green-500/30 pb-32">
        
        <div class="fixed inset-0 z-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:24px_24px]"></div>
        <div class="fixed inset-0 z-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_800px_at_50%_-30%,#064e3b,transparent)]"></div>

        <div class="max-w-5xl w-full z-10 space-y-12 pt-12 md:pt-24">
            
            <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-green-500 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors group font-mono uppercase tracking-widest">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
                </svg>
                KEMBALI KE BERANDA
            </a>

            <div class="space-y-4 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-8">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-green-500/30 bg-green-900/10 text-xs font-mono text-green-400 uppercase tracking-widest">
                        IT Solutions & Services
                    </span>
                    <span class="flex h-2 w-2 relative">
                        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75"></span>
                        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-green-500"></span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-xs text-green-500 font-mono tracking-widest uppercase">TOKO BUKA</span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-tech uppercase">One Computer</h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
                    Toko kami bergerak di bidang penjualan dan servis komputer dengan komitmen menyediakan produk original, harga terjangkau, dan layanan terpercaya.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
                
                <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-16">
                    
                    <section class="space-y-8">
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white font-tech flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></span>
                            01 // PRODUK DAN LAYANAN
                        </h2>
                        
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            {[
                                { t: "1. Penjualan Unit", d: "Menyediakan berbagai unit komputer, laptop, dan perangkat IT siap pakai untuk kebutuhan pribadi, sekolah, dan perkantoran, dengan pilihan spesifikasi yang dapat disesuaikan budget." },
                                { t: "2. Aksesoris & Sparepart", d: "Menyediakan berbagai aksesoris serta sparepart komputer dan laptop untuk menunjang performa, kenyamanan, dan perawatan perangkat, tersedia produk original maupun alternatif." },
